Other relevant sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as the paper discusses the theoretical underpinnings of deep nets and their applications in various fields.
